SUMMARY:Alice Olsthoorn
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:A true icon of the LGBTQ+ community and far beyond\n\nDJ. Artis
 t. Producer. Icon. Pretty much the perfect bio for Alice Olsthoorn in four
  words.\nBut make no mistake\, she deserves her own Bible. First\, the ele
 ctronically trained musician took TikTok then she took ESNS. Her music is 
 heavily inspired by queer rave culture. Brash\, extravagant\, transformati
 ve\, funny and hyper sexy. The answer to a white man’s stripes and stars
 . It’s Friday and we’re in love with Alice!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
