BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-058a2523ea45142f@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T130000Z
DTEND:20260612T140000Z
SUMMARY:Madra Salach (mostly Irish DJ set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Devastatingly beautiful folk band debuting a “Mostly Irish”
  DJ set\n\nFavourite act on this year’s line-up with a first ever DJ Set
 . A heart’s wish from The Floor! Especially because this will be a (most
 ly) Irish selection.\nFrom indie to traditionals to hip hop\, the Green Wa
 ve is real and it’s so much more than having a Guinness on a terrace in 
 your cycling kit. Listening to Madra Salach is an intense\, all encompassi
 ng experience. How could this possibly translate to a dancefloor? Only one
  way to discover. Get your Brits Out\, We’Re On A Mad One!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-b926149b7a85afb0@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T140000Z
DTEND:20260612T160000Z
