BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-5f52b1f1fd935990@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T160000Z
DTEND:20260612T170000Z
SUMMARY:Ko Kliko
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Electronic indie crusader on a mission\n\nKo Kliko stands for p
 ostpunk\, electroclash\, indie\, alternative pop and trends that can go ri
 ght in the trashcan.\nIf it is up to Cora Ziengs\, genres are boring. She 
 even has a successful alter ego playing house and jazz (Coco Coquelicot). 
 The passionate DJ is one of the founders of Relate Radio\, a stalwart with
 in the Music scene of Groningen and has made her way to festivals like ESN
 S and Lowlands. Not by giving in\, but by lashing out. The Floor can only 
 approve
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-c9bff651a770c02e@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T170000Z
DTEND:20260612T173000Z
SUMMARY:DJ St. Paul
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:The Floor manager who lets it all happen\n\nDJ St. Paul aka the
  pundit behind Pop-O-Matic\, aka the honcho of Let It Happen\, aka the chi
 ef facilitator of Best Kept Secret's The Floor.Paul isn’t a floor manage
 r like those at normal work environments\; it’s all play in his book. Ev
 ery year he invites an uncanny list of guests from all corners and crevice
 s of the music world – blasting the biggest hits\, the most vital niches
  & subcultures\, the juiciest of deep cuts\, and everything inbetween at T
