BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-64e6bb79629f6a65@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T190000Z
DTEND:20260612T200000Z
SUMMARY:Ineffekt
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Bass-heavy but light-hearted producer on the rise\n\nMasterful 
 Dutch producer gaining international momentum with his bass-heavy but ligh
 t-hearted sound.\nAfter Sammy Virji and MEGRA before him\, this years UK B
 ass inspired golden hour at The Floor will go to our own Ineffekt. His tra
 cks are frequently supported by producers like Four Tet and platforms such
  as the BBC\, but are just as easily the main ingredient for eclectic DJ
 ’s like host DJ St. Paul who couldn’t be more proud to present this tr
 ue gem of an artist. More than an icon. At the exact heart of the festival
  this will be the soundtrack to your new found hopes and dreams. No refund
  for lost chagrin!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-82bccf7f1b75d99e@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T200000Z
DTEND:20260612T210000Z
