BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-cf977cff4ece1d88@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T210000Z
DTEND:20260612T220000Z
SUMMARY:Nymfo B2B Zohar
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:A highly anticipated communion of forward-thinking club sonics.
 \n\nZohar & Nymfo are bringing together two distinct\, complementary force
 s in electronic music.\nKnown for her technical refinement and mixing wiza
 rdry\, Zohar is always pushing listeners into new territory. With releases
  on labels like Metalheadz and Hospital Records\, Nymfo is a beloved mains
 tay in the jungle and rave scene. With this unique B2B the two artists are
  celebrating their magnificent joint release on Dekmantel and a communion 
 of souls united in forward thinking club sonics
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-e588f0a94ecae3a5@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260612T220000Z
DTEND:20260612T230000Z
SUMMARY:DJ St. Paul
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:The Floor manager who lets it all happen\n\nDJ St. Paul aka the
  pundit behind Pop-O-Matic\, aka the honcho of Let It Happen\, aka the chi
 ef facilitator of Best Kept Secret's The Floor.Paul isn’t a floor manage
 r like those at normal work environments\; it’s all play in his book. Ev
 ery year he invites an uncanny list of guests from all corners and crevice
