BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-51197067d1fde37e@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T131500Z
DTEND:20260613T141500Z
SUMMARY:KROON (Kypski Live Set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Legendary beatmaker and turntablist with his latest crowning ac
 hievement\n\nKROON is an electronic masterclass of Kypski\, Kubus and Hajo
 \, that started at Best Kept Secret.\nMythical Tilburg musician and gentle
  soul Hajo Krijger sadly passed away in the summer of 2025. Such a shame t
 hat he could’t live to see the release of the KROON album this year. The
  live show at The Floor is an ode to him and the music the three producers
  made together. Kypski will perform their unique blend of early dubstep\, 
 blistering electronics and gritty beats live with also some classic jungle
  and hip hop in the mix. As much a memorial as it is a celebration of life
  and music. Let us all together be the heavy head that wears the crown.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-dd93a3b39f00d421@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T141500Z
DTEND:20260613T143000Z
