BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-b2d7e5dee64c7cde@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T160000Z
DTEND:20260613T170000Z
SUMMARY:Lucky Done Gone B2B Sef
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Two likeminded artists taking us on a joyous safari\n\nOnce in 
 a lifetime back-to-back between two spiritually connected Best Kept Secret
  ‘26 artists.\nProducer and DJ Lucky Done Gone casually plays that sense
  of euphoria back in your life. Rapper\, musician and two-time The Floor D
 J Sef guides your emotions like the chief conductor of song he is. A “Fe
 el Good Inc” some primates in the Beeksonian Mountains are already whisp
 ering about this unique collaboration.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-336872e103682445@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T170000Z
DTEND:20260613T173000Z
