BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-11f17c3ab13a3551@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T173000Z
DTEND:20260613T190000Z
SUMMARY:Marie Davidson (DJ set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Canadian furnisher of floor fillers with extra long DJ set\n\nM
 arie Davidson is like an ongoing subscription to your favourite dance floo
 r. Her music works\, all the fucking time.\nPitchfork called her 2025 albu
 m City of Clowns “bangers-only art that smashes binaries”. The Canadia
 n artist is a war poet\, a power plant providing much needed energy in dys
 topian times. Together with the production duties of Soulwax this makes fo
 r furious dancing. So proud to have her over for an extra extended DJ set.
  Give me passion\, give me more\, I want your ass on The Floor!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-01202bd4a910c382@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T190000Z
DTEND:20260613T200000Z
SUMMARY:Aili & Orson (Japanese DJ Set)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Electro-pop duo visiting Japanese roots in unique DJ Set\n\nAil
 i is a Belgium-Japanese electro-pop duo consisting of Aili Maruyama and Or
 son Wouters.\nTheir instant musical chemistry led to a playful and spontan
 eous approach to songwriting\, combining electronic beats\, samples\, and 
 Aili's unique blend of Japanese vocals. A highlight within the recent outp
 ut of the infamous Eskimo Recordings label. Who needs a game of football a
 gainst the Japanese when you dance to their music too!!
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-a212e02de08eb473@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T200000Z
DTEND:20260613T203000Z
