BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-8d42e45167fe80c5@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T203000Z
DTEND:20260613T213000Z
SUMMARY:Oceanic (Maximal Minimalism)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Beloved DJ and electronic musician debuting a set of minimalist
  music only\n\nGifted producer and DJ Oceanic holds a maximum love for min
 imalist music. His work is as ambient as the air surrounding the head of Z
 arafa the giraffe. It was only a matter of time before this sonic adventur
 er would try his hands at a set consisting of (classical) minimalist music
  only. Steve Reich\, Louis Andriessen\, Julius Eastman. Beauty lies in the
  details only the heart can hear. The Floor is proud to present Oceanic tr
 ying out his first ever Maximal Minimalism experiment.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:best-kept-secret-2026-a7a2378f348f8790@second-brain.local
DTSTAMP:20260611T103410Z
DTSTART:20260613T213000Z
DTEND:20260613T223000Z
