SUMMARY:Abiba Sokoto
LOCATION:The Shore
DESCRIPTION:Expressive house\, soul and jazz selections\n\nThe warm selecti
 ons of Abiba Sokoto are an ode to the Black music continuum.\nSpanning hou
 se\, electro\, soul and jazz. Abiba showcases her wide-ranging taste throu
 gh her Operator Radio residency\, ALLBLUE\, as well as across numerous rad
 io appearances from RRFM to Future Intel.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
